Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togashi's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.57,0:00:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! After all, they've shacked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.59,0:00:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shacked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to have a peek?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.83,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shacking up isn't all that shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My master merely shares a hideout\Nwith Dark Flame Master
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under the terms of their formal contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are not living the\Nscandalous life you imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, Togashi asked us\Nnot to talk about it at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're in high school!\NThey're boyfriend and girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're living together!\NDoesn't it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that bothers me\Nis a decrepit non-sorcerer like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am busy. Now be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Deko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.57,0:00:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am creating an adventure log for my fallen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.14,0:00:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,comrades who have retreated \Nfrom the front line.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adventure log?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's assembling lesson notes\Nfor classmates who weren't at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:00:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you stay behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested, Kumin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.05,0:01:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A couple in love, living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet their hearts flutter when they\Nmake eye contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they have little cuddles\Nwhen nobody's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet they even sneak kisses\Nwhen Little Sister isn't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.85,0:01:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:16.51,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,LOVE LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:18.64,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,LOVE LOVE LOVE LOVE LOVE LOVE LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet! Be quiet! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it does bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:03:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dark wave motions prevent me\Nfrom seeing my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master... Where are you, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Face it. It seriously bothers you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finished off those lesson notes\Nincredibly fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I see Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's either testing the wind direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or he is ordering the dark ones\Nto assemble for a new battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he's taking in the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I forgot to take it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I believe it was Rikka's turn today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. I've \Nalways done the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Dolphin Ring Striker
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work. She's \Nthe one who suggested it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:46.91,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,BADDY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The Wicked Lord's chaotic trance\Ndark hot pot is served.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're calling it dark hot pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka, my big brother and I will take care\Nof all the cooking from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:04:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please assign me a different mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only started assigning chores\Nbecause of her messes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were supposed to die then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use the vacuum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! Did you buy those?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I did not "buy" anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was preordained that these\Nshould fall into my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are so cool! Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could use these to \Nplay ghost busters too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, you look so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your own vacuuming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But these must have been expensive.\NI'm surprised you had the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.55,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,EVERY WHICH WAY BANK\NRIKKA TAKANASHI
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toka mentioned that she'd deposited\Nyour monthly allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka. No, Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:05:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you please show me your\Ngold documentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Wicked Lord Shingan's\Nmost secret secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot disclose that secret, even to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show it to me, Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you open it, all the evil \Ncontained therein will escape
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and spread over the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just show it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Power Level: 150,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is more powerful than the Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to your sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how they act at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be sure just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, couples don't\Nact lovey-dovey all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, someone's moved\Ninto the apartment above.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:50.32,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,PAKIRA\NFRESH MARKET
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you really planning to ride out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe rest of the month on less than 1000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of Wicked Lord Shingan's abilities\Nis the empty rupture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic of Wicked Lord Shingan\Nwho dwells within me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can maintain my bodily functions\Nwithout nourishment for years...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...enabling life activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NEW PRODUCT!!!\NArabiki Crunchy Sausages
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a sample?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? You are hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'll take two bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going out to shop together for food\Nfor supper is much more romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dragging me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NA sign said 'no roller skates in the store.'
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My foe could attack at any time,\Nbut I'm ready for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will topple that pile of \Ncandy and block them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I will immediately \Ndestroy the lighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when they have been blinded,\NI'll finish them with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Offense and defense as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look how late it is. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.38,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CUMIN
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, we must purchase Kumin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need any. Put it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? C'mon, we need to buy Kumin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:07:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Dekomori?\NMaybe they have Dekomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a spice, dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are cumin seeds.\NEffective for putting monsters to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cumin is used for making curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't make authentic curry at our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The usual roux cubes will suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have something against Kumin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that. C'mon, we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to have split up with Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I will have the blue crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.26,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,MYSTERY JEWEL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done? Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, I must go to verify the \Ncondition of a singularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At your leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it back home by supper time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear it on the name of\Nthe Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Master summons me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way! Dekomori is on her way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nice that they're such good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although they didn't look that lovey-dovey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been going out for six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the time most couples are\Nsupposed to be at their busiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But look at the state of them. I suspect...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...marital burnout!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burnout paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, Morisummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to respect your senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, you're burning out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about Takanashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're boyfriend and girlfriend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've sounded out your feelings\Nfor one another, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.76,0:08:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel excitement \Nwhen you're together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you hold hands and\Ngaze into one another's eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-that has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't changed a bit in the last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you seem totally oblivious too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oblivious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spied on you two yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you looked more like father\Nand daughter than a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like grampa and grandkid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling grampa?\NYou were tailing us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you don't like cumin, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've shacked up! Togashi,\Nyou're living with your girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you ever bill and \Ncoo like normal couples?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're wrong about\Nthe marital burnout thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that refers to a couple growing\Ndispassionate about one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In our case, me and Rikka,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we haven't even gotten to \Nthe hand-holding stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. So, the marital burnout thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...really doesn't apply to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does that make you so angry anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you start going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:09:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you go on a boat date?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're saying that New Year's Eve\Nand Valentine's Day went by...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you still haven't \Neven held hands yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're choking me, Nibutani.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait, Nibutani!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togashi, look what they did to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kazari Kannagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, my name is Kazari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kannagi knows everything to do with romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll give you good advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to keep me and Rikka\Nliving together a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that. I didn't tell her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only told her that your love life\Nisn't going so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka is your girlfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh, well, it's kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why hide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two have been famous\Never since Year One.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you're having problems with Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be my big chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually like girls.\NAnd I'm infatuated with Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell her because if she found out,\Nthat would be the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my rival? I hope \Nthat is the end of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But all joking aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, please give me your cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The best thing to do is ask her on a date,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nset the right mood, and see how she reacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what are you doing with my phone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending mail. "Will you please go out\Non a date with me this Sunday?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I have something important to talk\Nto you about." Send.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was kind of exciting because\Nit was like telling Rikka I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may look calm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but every girl waits for the boy\Nto make the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi can't say what's on her mind,\Npartly due to her syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to coax her out of her shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, you could have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.38,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Sender: Rikka Takanashi\NROGER THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Rikka and I, \Nalbeit unintentionally...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...made a date for Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Water Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka, that's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The use of this robe is only permitted\Nfor special ceremonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Is something special happening today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me first. What is our destination?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a place you \Nkind of wanted to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gasp! Are you reading my thoughts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a firm grip?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Releasing evil skill formula.\NDeployment prep complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, we have a green light. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem, other than poor visibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can \Ndo about your visibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to concentrate on safe driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Your death is also my death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scaring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, the Wicked Lord\NShingan is all-powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He allows me to see everything,\Ndespite my visibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can even see into your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time you \Nmentioned that ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you are thinking,\N"Whoa! I'm breaking the sound barrier!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I am a virtual whirlwind of\Nlightning speed!" Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind turbines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will rotate the windmills using dark power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:13:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join me, Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:13:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. We just need to unite\Nour dark powers as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked Lord Fire Dragon wave motion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw an internet video showing a windmill\Nbeing destroyed by gale-force winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.63,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SAZANAMI AQUARIUM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh. It's the reincarnation of R'lyeh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember how you said\Nyou wanted to see a real dolphin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Kyle is a genius.\NHe is in the form of a fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I suspect he is actually\Na dark warrior in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen him around recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dear Ancient Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may look calm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but every girl waits for the boy\Nto make the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. Since we're here, \Njust the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would you like to hold hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, you don't have to if you're too shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that we've only touched pinkies...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.85,0:15:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since we started going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, penguins! Penguins!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nautilus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. "Nau-t-lus."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I once seriously wanted to attend\NMiskatonic University...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the Mu civilization was never\Nan existing continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Mister Kyle only existed\Nin the Japanese version.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such incredible speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The speed to tear through magical dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if you would like to give signals to\Nthe dolphin, show me your flippers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, that girl there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you please tell us \Nyour name and your age?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm Rikka Takanashi. I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in grade six.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell her that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look hard at the dolphin's face,\Nand sway your head from side to side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Dolphin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Shall I dry your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next let's get the \Ntraining lady teach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...how to give the signal to jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, point upward with your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, touch your right hand \Nto your left shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To give the signal, we will count to three...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,0:16:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then you must raise your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin. One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dolphin is at my bidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, diving beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! A Japanese giant salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't much different \Nfrom the norm either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to coax her out of her shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shakey shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you have this with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This returns from vending machines\Nevery single time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chosen 10 yen coin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I don't get excited \Nabout every little thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh. Did I miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it isn't a serrated \N10 yen coin after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so old, the edge got smoothed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing. You have lost \Nyour place in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:18:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has merely lost its place in the\Nvending machine system.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still good currency.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then it would lose its\Npredominance as the Chosen One.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today was fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dolphin tore through the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we even held hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yeah. I'll hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you can hold, hand-holding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still don't understand it that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.01,0:18:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made the love pact with you,\Nso we are boyfriend and girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still don't have the\Nslightest idea what lovers are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about it makes my head confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we are lovers,\Nregular physical contact is inevitable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I searched for the meaning of lovers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's still unclear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I searched the net, but it was gibberish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does "Common-law couples are not
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nnecessarily designated as lovers" even mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally different from my contract\Nwith Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean you didn't want the love pact?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that! I do want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know what I should be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm certain\Nthat something must change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can say one thing with certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fun day is coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will soon go home.\NTogether to the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing could make me happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So happy in fact, that I fear I've peaked,\Nand am now marked for death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's turning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our powers worked on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wicked Lord Shingan \Nis definitely invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! But The Dark Flame Master\Nis second-most invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it isn't that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am impressed, Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are indeed the one, I,\NDark Flame Master, expected you to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The contract you and I are bound to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is not the so-called lover's \Npact of the mundanes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the lover's pact of\Nthe Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.43,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, we need not feel\Nthe obligation to be manipulated
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the so-called conventional\Nwisdom of commoners!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may fulfill our contract as we see fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am certain we can fulfill this pact!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For we are the Wicked Lord Shingan\Nand Dark Flame Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You turned the windmills and came home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're really okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that Rikka still needs to be Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a lot better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you're okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kannagi gave me some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that if a couple keeps\Nputting everything off...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it nearly always gives an interloper\Nthe chance to come between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oof, oof.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna see my magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be Continued
